1000                  maximum number of iterations
1.0e-7 		      absolute tolerance
1.0e-7                relative tolerance		      
1                     stopping test (1=our own, 2=delta_x, 3=gsl grad)
1                     write summary? (not 1 == don't write)
gsl.out               summary file (max 20 characters)		      
1                     write iteration summary (not 1 == don't write)
